org.cougaar.core.blackboard
Class SubscriptionWatcher

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.core.blackboard.SubscriptionWatcher

public class SubscriptionWatcher
extends java.lang.Object

A callback for BlackboardService.registerInterest(org.cougaar.core.blackboard.SubscriptionWatcher) subscription or alarm activity.

On the signalNotify(int) callback, the watcher should schedule itself to run in a separate thread, e.g. by using the ThreadService.

Most of this could likely be removed and replaced with a simple Schedulable.start(), since most clients don't check the signalNotify(int) "event" and the Subscriber has a Subscriber.wasClientActivity() method that's equivalent to clearSignal().
